data.description: Catch a glimpse of this charming one and a half story 1,864 sq ft cottage, sitting on 0.88 acre in North Union Township.  This home offers a blend of scenic beauty and modern updates and features two first floor bedrooms, new architectural shingle roof in 2018, an updated kitchen and bath completed in 2018, ductless mini-split installed in 2021. The fenced yard is perfect for the pet lovers and outdoor enjoyment, providing  secure and private space. Ideal for those seeking a blend of comfort and style, this cottage is a unique find in a picturesque setting.
